name: Cargolux 747-8R7F [LX-VCH] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Nice to see Cargolux again! Can't believe it's been almost a year since I last posted one of these guys. Here we have LX-VCH, a 3 year old 747-8F taxiing up close on Romeo and departing runway 35R, with some great engine sounds. ATC is included throughout; enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
